PowerSigns: give your signs Power!

Quick summary of different PowerSigns:

Push: push an adjacent row of blocks with the material specified by one block, can push any direction but towards the sign itself

Pull: pull on a row of blocks with the material specified from far away towards the sign

Activate: attempt to activate a row of signs as if they were other PowerSigns

Activate_long: activates a single sign from a distance

Cannon: launch a TNT stored in an adjacent Dispenser, specifying an angle and power when launching from the front of the dispenser

swap and copy: sign text manipulation PowerSign

inv(push and pull): push and pull blocks....from a chest or dispenser!

fling: launch yourself into the air 

